text_blocks.text:
means the actual or imminent occurrence of an event which endangers or threatens the safety or health of any communities or persons in Tuvalu, or which destroys or damages, any property in Tuvalu, arising from:
* a cyclone;
* a flood;
* tsunami;
* a drought;
* an air disaster;
* a maritime disaster;
* a major civil accident (such as major fire or explosion);
* a plague or epidemic; or
* any other similar natural or man-made event,
